Galley#
Once they were called slaves, today they are called employees...
What are we talking about? About the human engine of your very first 
transport units. Besides the slaves you need of course some whip-wielding
taskmasters to raise the troops´ morale. But then, theoretically,
the conquest of all those new worlds shall commence. 
Those small warships, equipped with both oars and sails, are  
capable of transporting one single ground-based unit.


